== Release notes ==
Single file torrent of exact installer from official website.

The main highlight of Messenger Plus Live v4.50 is skinning. You can now change the appearance of your Messenger, rapidly and securely. All the pictures can be modified, the windows re-shaped and the elements re-colorized. Of course, skinning is only one of the many new things offered by this version. The Preferences panel has been re-designed, Script developers can now enjoy new API functions as well as a much better built-in , the Log Viewer has been completely reworked and the Contact List Clean-Up is now upgraded along with many other improvements.

